</aside>
</header>
<section class="entry">
<p>TRACK co-sponsored this video which promotes birth registration through civil registration. This film features input from government, UNHCR and NGO representatives on the importance of civil registration and the key elements of the 2013 UNHCR Executive Committee  (ExCom) Conclusion on the topic. The UNHCR ExCom is the head committee that makes recommendations. Civil registration is part of [&hellip;]</p>
</section>
