<aside class="post-meta">
<ul>
<li class="post-author">
<span class="img-wrap"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/bcc2f6dca93e18525cc7140cc4f6335b?s=30&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D30&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-30 photo' height='30' width='30'/></span>
<span class="small">by</span>
